dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Racine County, WI 2017
dc_description_s: These data layers represent hydrography for Racine County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, 'Racine_Hydro_2017.gdb'. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are 'Racine_HydroLine_2017' and 'Racine_HydroPoly_2017'.
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most current data available, please visit: https://data-racinecounty.opendata.arcgis.com/
